caption.text:
Ori and the Blind Forest: Definitive Edition
Data de Lançamento, 27 Setembro.
Game - Switch.

A floresta de Nibel está morrendo. Depois que uma forte tempestade desencadeia uma série de eventos devastadores, Ori deve viajar para encontrar coragem e enfrentar um inimigo sombrio para salvar a floresta de Nibel. Ori e a Floresta Cega conta a história de um jovem órfão destinado a heroísmo, através de um impressionante jogo de plataformas de ação, criado pela Moon Studios. Com obras de arte pintadas à mão, performance meticulosamente animada de personagens, uma partitura totalmente orquestrada e dezenas de novos recursos na Definitive Edition, Ori and the Blind Forest explora uma história profundamente emocional sobre amor e sacrifício e a esperança que existe em todos nós.

19. Link’s Admires “...Tarin says there is nothing beyond the sea, but I believe there must be something over there... When I discovered you, Link, my heart skipped a beat!
...If I was a seagull I would fly as far as I could! I would fly to far away places and sing for many people! ...” Marin from ‘The Legend of Zelda: Link’s Awakening’ is a sweet girl who dreams of leaving the island and spread joy to people through her singing, and meeting Link only strengthens that dream. Top sales game Nintendo yang terpilih minggu ini adalah “New Super Mario Bros U. Deluxe” ✨

New Super Mario Bros U. Deluxe merupakan game versi lebih baik dari versi WII U lhoo. Hal ini karena Nintendo telah menggabungkan game New Super Mario Bros U. dan New Super Luigi U. menjadi satu game 🤩. Game ini juga telah rilis di Nintendo Switch pada tanggal 10 Januari 2019. Sejak bulan Maret 2019, penjualan game New Super Mario Bros U. Deluxe telah mencapai angka 4,1 juta! 😲

New Super Mario Bros U. Deluxe bergenre platform game seperti halnya game Super Mario Bros yang kalian kenal selama ini 😉. Layaknya ciri khas game Super Mario Bros, kalian akan berpetualang sebagai Mario atau Luigi untuk menyelamatkan Peach dari Bowser (again) 😅. Kali ini kalian tidak hanya berpetualang sendirian untuk menyelamatkan Peach karena game ini dapat dimainkan hingga 4 orang sekaligus dalam game ini 😃. Kalian juga dapat memilih nih ingin berperan sebagai Mario, Luigi, Toad, Toadette, atau Nabbit di mana mereka memiliki kelebihan dan kekurangan masing-masing 👌. Oleh karena itu, semakin banyak pemainnya maka kalian semakin akan melengkapi. 🙈

Nah jika kalian ingin tahu keseruan New Super Mario Bros U. Deluxe, saat ini gamenya sudah dapat disewa di NSRent ya!! Segera cek ketersediaan game ini dan koleksi game lainnya di bio Instagram atau hubungi NSRent via DM yaa ✨

caption.text:
So I’ve seen a lot of people upset about Luigi not being in Mario Kart Tour and rightfully so. However these gacha games are always adding characters and putting them as spotlights for the weekly banner. And what better way to kick off October with its first new banner being LUIGI who has a game coming out later that month! Also these mobile games like to throw holiday events especially for Halloween (Think of Dragalia Lost for example) and a Luigi’s Mansion themed banner would be PERFECT for a Halloween event. Plus this is a perfect advertising opportunity for Luigi’s Mansion 3! To show you what this would look like I made 2 mock-up screens of the banner and description like they did for Pauline. I think they would add Luigi (obviously) his Poltergust 4000 Kart from Mario Kart DS a Luigi’s Mansion themed glider and either bring back the Luigi’s Mansion course from the DS or make a brand new course based on the hotel from the new game. So anyways what do you guys think about this idea?
.
.
.
.
